OL,3,CFamily accuse Met Police of failures
OL,4,Cafter gay student found dead in hotel
OL,6,FThe family of Ed Cornes, a 19-year-old
OL,7,Fgay student found dead in a London
OL,8,Fhotel, say police failures ` driven by
OL,9,Fhomophobia ` meant the circumstances
OL,10,Fof his death were never properly
OL,11,Finvestigated.
OL,13,FEd was just two days into his first
OL,14,Fterm at University College London when
OL,15,Fhe died in October 2021.
