OL,6,FNearly four years on, his mother,
OL,7,FMiriam Blythe, says she still has
OL,8,Fquestions over how or why he died `
OL,9,Fand she has no confidence in the
OL,10,FMetropolitan Police or its handling of
OL,11,Fthe case.
OL,13,FShe accuses officers of focusing on
OL,14,Fhis sexuality, of failing to interview
OL,15,Fkey witnesses, and of allowing crucial
OL,16,Fevidence to be lost while the death
OL,17,Fwas still being treated as a potential
OL,18,Fmurder.
