OL,6,FBecause what followed, Miriam says,
OL,7,Fwas a police investigation riddled
OL,8,Fwith failures and shaped by
OL,9,Finstitutional homophobia at Britain's
OL,10,Fbiggest police force. An internal
OL,11,Freview later found 27 failings.
OL,13,FThe Metropolitan Police was found to
OL,14,Fbe institutionally homophobic by a
OL,15,Flandmark report in March 2023. A
OL,16,Freview carried out by Baroness Louise
OL,17,FCasey, who spent a year investigating
OL,18,Fthe force in the wake of the murder of
OL,19,FSarah Everard.
