OL,6,F"They treated us appallingly," Miriam
OL,7,Fsaid. "They had no cause of death, and
OL,8,Fthey refused to interview his friends.
OL,9,FSo they also had no idea who Ed was."
OL,11,F"They focused in on him being gay and
OL,12,Fwhether he took drugs. His lifestyle
OL,13,Fand sexuality," she said.
OL,15,FEd's body was found in a basement room
OL,16,Fof a hotel in King's Cross, central
OL,17,FLondon, around five minutes from his
OL,18,Fhalls of residence.
OL,20,FOther students said he was "very
OL,21,Fdrunk" that evening.
